  <h3>For tracking to builds on multiple machines running Hudson.</h3>
  <div class="content">
    <p>The Hudson Global Dashboard is an idea that stems from the <a href="http://www.panic.com/blog/2010/03/the-panic-status-board/">Panic Board</a>. We had a scenario where we had multiple machines running Hudson, and for knowing at-a-glance the status of a build we relied either on build lights (USB lights, changing red to green depending on build) or CCMenu.</p>
